Class KafkaSimplePartitioner

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.tsd.KafkaSimplePartitioner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    kafka.producer.Partitioner

    public class KafkaSimplePartitioner
extends Object
implements kafka.producer.Partitioner
    Simple partitioner class. It assumes that our key is a positive integer based on the hash code. If you pass in a string that can't parse to a Long, then the partitioner will throw an exception.
